00:40:59,820 --> 00:41:00,613
Tata!

466
00:41:14,746 --> 00:41:17,998
Tata!

467
00:41:22,042 --> 00:41:23,793
Pricaj engleski duso...

468
00:41:24,877 --> 00:41:28,213
Imala sam ruzan san.
Nisi jedina...Hoces casu mleka?

469
00:41:45,139 --> 00:41:47,766
Dolazi mama.

470
00:42:09,570 --> 00:42:11,988
Poljubac za srecan put?
