471
00:42:12,197 --> 00:42:14,573
Treba mi uteha!
-.

472
00:42:14,824 --> 00:42:15,658
zdravo, Charlie.

473
00:42:15,866 --> 00:42:18,493
Izgubio sam trku,
a tvoja zena nece da me tesi.

474
00:42:22,912 --> 00:42:24,121
Laku noc.

475
00:42:24,412 --> 00:42:28,082
- Vidi sta sam ti donela.
Nisam zaboravila.

476
00:42:30,125 --> 00:42:33,210
- Laku noc svima!

477
00:42:45,050 --> 00:42:45,968
Charlie!

478
00:42:48,302 --> 00:42:50,053
Ti nisi Charlie.

479
00:42:51,805 --> 00:42:53,431
Gde je Charlie?

480
00:43:04,812 --> 00:43:08,690
Jos uvek joj nisi rekao?
- Zasto da joj kvarim zabavu?

481
00:43:08,898 --> 00:43:13,192
Zasto kvaris sebi?
- Zato sto sam cudan.

482
00:43:13,693 --> 00:43:16,236
Potrosio sam godinu dana
pokusavajuci da napisem knjigu.

483
00:43:16,695 --> 00:43:19,863
A nema nikoga ko
bi je objavio.

484
00:43:20,113 --> 00:43:22,948
Nisi uopste cudan,
samo si naivan.

485
00:43:23,157 --> 00:43:25,032
Poznavao sam
jednog izdavaca...

486
00:43:25,241 --> 00:43:26,284
...on nikada nije citao rukopise.

487
00:43:26,451 --> 00:43:28,702
Samo bi ih pomirisao..

488
00:43:30,828 --> 00:43:32,871
Ako bi mirisali na,
smece...

489
00:43:33,079 --> 00:43:35,748
...on bi ih objavljivao.

490
00:43:36,331 --> 00:43:38,207
Znas li sta je tajna
uspeha?

491
00:43:38,583 --> 00:43:42,127
Osrednjost, momce.
Da bi bio bogat pisac...

492
00:43:42,543 --> 00:43:44,795
...moras da ispunjavas tri
uslova.

493
00:43:45,128 --> 00:43:49,298
Da budes bogat,
grub i pokvaren.

494
00:44:27,321 --> 00:44:29,363
"Subotnje novine"
su kupile moj feljton..

495
00:44:29,572 --> 00:44:31,615
...za 15 000$!

496
00:44:32,990 --> 00:44:34,366
Bravo!

497
00:44:34,533 --> 00:44:35,408
Hvala.

498
00:44:38,952 --> 00:44:41,829
Feljton za 15000$,
i to bez poreza!

499
00:44:42,038 --> 00:44:43,705
Mogao bi da napravis
neku zabavu.

500
00:44:55,879 --> 00:44:58,589
Charlie, idi do policije.

501
00:44:58,798 --> 00:45:00,049
- Zasto?
- Priveli su...

502
00:45:00,216 --> 00:45:01,925
...neku ludu Amerikanku.

503
00:45:02,133 --> 00:45:03,550
Zaustavila je,
saobracaj...

504
00:45:03,759 --> 00:45:06,427
...jer je uskocila u
fontanu.

505
00:45:06,636 --> 00:45:08,303
Je li to vazna prica?
- Ne.

506
00:45:08,470 --> 00:45:10,389
Znas koliko Amerikanci u Parzu
vole da citaju...

507
00:45:10,555 --> 00:45:12,681
...o  Amerikancima
u Parzu.

508
00:45:13,390 --> 00:45:16,558
U redu. Kako se zove?
- Helen Wills.

509
00:45:19,268 --> 00:45:20,769
To je moja cura.

510
00:45:34,611 --> 00:45:36,862
Ako me ne poznajes..

511
00:45:37,405 --> 00:45:39,948
