"U bolesti i u zdravlju,

512
00:45:40,115 --> 00:45:41,615
dok nas smrt ne rastavi"...

513
00:45:41,824 --> 00:45:43,409
Znas da se lako prehladis.

514
00:45:43,658 --> 00:45:46,410
Idi kuci i presvuci se.
- Ne mozemo kuci.

515
00:45:46,702 --> 00:45:48,744
Vicki  je u Dhingu.
- Opet ?

516
00:45:48,994 --> 00:45:51,371
Zar nije bolje da bude u
otmenom bistrou...

517
00:45:51,579 --> 00:45:52,747
...nego sama kod kuce?

518
00:45:55,999 --> 00:45:57,875
Hoce li izaci u novinama?

519
00:45:58,501 --> 00:46:01,044
Jos jedna luda Amerikanka
skocila u jos jednu, lepu fontanu?

520
00:46:01,293 --> 00:46:03,170
