00:47:37,435 --> 00:47:40,020
Ne. Da me nacrta.
Mene ne pitate za pice?

543
00:47:40,228 --> 00:47:44,273
Ja sam je izvukao iz zatvora.

544
00:48:41,265 --> 00:48:45,810
- Engleski,molim te...

545
00:48:48,687 --> 00:48:51,271
Hocu da ti pokazem...Mama je...

546
00:48:51,730 --> 00:48:53,773
Ne pola- pola.

547
00:48:53,940 --> 00:48:56,441
Samo engleski.

548
00:48:56,775 --> 00:48:58,651
Gledaj,tata!

549
00:48:59,694 --> 00:49:02,445
Cekaj.
Nisi me poljubila.

550
00:49:07,198 --> 00:49:08,991
Charlie..!
- Barney!

