00:49:09,700 --> 00:49:10,992
Hoces da vidis nesto lepo?

552
00:49:25,251 --> 00:49:27,419
Mlada je za 
bocu, zar ne?

553
00:49:27,711 --> 00:49:30,421
To je zbog poda.
Niko ne moze da igra...

554
00:49:30,670 --> 00:49:33,380
...po ovakom podu.
Jesi li dobro?

555
00:49:33,839 --> 00:49:37,341
Zao mi je.
- Reci joj nesto lepo.

556
00:49:38,216 --> 00:49:40,135
Odlicno je , mala.
Sjajno.

557
00:49:40,302 --> 00:49:41,719
Sef hoce da 
intervijuisem...

558
00:49:41,927 --> 00:49:43,053
...verenicu nekog kralja...

559
00:49:43,261 --> 00:49:44,637
...Imam vazan sastanak.

560
00:49:44,846 --> 00:49:45,971
Zameni me,molim te.
Vazi ?

561
00:49:46,305 --> 00:49:47,848
Zena se zove Lorraine Quarl.

562
00:49:48,306 --> 00:49:49,724
- Ko je ona?

563
00:49:50,433 --> 00:49:51,850
Dama iz visokog drustva.

564
00:49:52,684 --> 00:49:54,476
Zdravo, mala.
Imas odlican nastup.

565
00:49:54,893 --> 00:49:56,978
Imas odlican nastup..

566
00:49:57,770 --> 00:49:59,646
...samo poboljsaj zavrsnicu.

567
00:50:00,606 --> 00:50:03,607
Imas odlicnu zavrsnicu duso.

568
00:50:03,857 --> 00:50:05,358
Dodji da te zagrlim.

569
00:50:10,528 --> 00:50:11,570
Gospodine Wills.

