Izvinite.

573
00:50:28,623 --> 00:50:30,582
Treba mi pice.

574
00:50:31,582 --> 00:50:34,208
Len.
- Kao i uvek, gospodjice?

575
00:50:38,003 --> 00:50:39,128
Parz je divan...

576
00:50:39,420 --> 00:50:41,671
Amerikanke vole Francuze..

577
00:50:41,838 --> 00:50:43,757
Francuzi vole Amerikanke..

578
00:50:43,923 --> 00:50:44,882
...cene su previsoke...

579
00:50:45,132 --> 00:50:47,050
Jos uvek nisam izabrala, svog,
 buduceg supruga.

580
00:50:48,842 --> 00:50:51,594
Mozda ce to biti barmen.
Talentovan je...

581
00:50:51,802 --> 00:50:53,471
Vidim. Davali ste intervijue...

582
00:50:54,179 --> 00:50:56,472
Poslednji pre sat vremena.

583
