Bio je to veoma kratak
 interviju.

584
00:51:01,516 --> 00:51:03,810
Za vas imam vremena.

585
00:51:05,228 --> 00:51:07,520
Prvi put ste u Parzu?

586
00:51:07,687 --> 00:51:09,271
- Ne, nije..

587
00:51:09,563 --> 00:51:13,441
Zasto ste onda dosli u Parz?
