00:51:33,286 --> 00:51:37,622
Prvi brak iz ljubavi... 
nije urodio plodom.

595
00:51:38,331 --> 00:51:41,208
Drugi brak..zbog novca,
takodje neplodan...

596
00:51:41,416 --> 00:51:43,501
Osim u vezi novca i imena.

597
00:51:44,085 --> 00:51:46,127
Treci brak zbog titule..
takodje neplodan.

598
00:51:48,712 --> 00:51:50,672
Cetvrti brak je
 bio najburniji.

599
00:51:51,756 --> 00:51:55,049
To je to, zasad...

600
00:51:56,008 --> 00:51:58,969
Da li je bilo dece?
- Ne.

