00:52:00,219 --> 00:52:02,428
To je moj jedini prilog
covecanstvu.

602
00:52:06,598 --> 00:52:08,516
Vec sam vam pomenula
 da sam neplodna...

603
00:52:12,393 --> 00:52:13,852
Zar necete to zapisati?

