00:52:14,019 --> 00:52:15,937
Interviju je odavno zavrsen.

605
00:52:17,187 --> 00:52:18,397
Hvala vam.

606
00:52:19,772 --> 00:52:21,315
Gladna sam.
Sta kazete za veceru?

607
00:52:21,524 --> 00:52:23,942
Nisam na listi bogatih.

608
00:52:24,150 --> 00:52:25,693
Ja sam samo
ubogi novinar...

609
00:52:25,901 --> 00:52:29,279
Ne brinite.

610
00:52:29,487 --> 00:52:31,113
Vecera je na racun mog
cetvrtog muza.

611
00:52:31,321 --> 00:52:33,197
A stacemo sa..?
- G-dine Wills...

612
00:52:33,406 --> 00:52:36,283
...u Americi placaju 50 $
na sat...da bi me slusali.

613
00:52:51,083 --> 00:52:53,251
Charles...
-  Claude.

614
00:52:53,543 --> 00:52:54,961
Kako si, Marion?
- Dobro.

615
00:53:05,216 --> 00:53:08,677
Ovo je sestra moje supruge
i njen muz...

616
00:53:16,974 --> 00:53:19,934
Claude je tuzilac.
- Da ?

617
00:53:20,143 --> 00:53:23,769
Nadam se da nista nisam zgresila.

618
00:53:27,772 --> 00:53:29,899
G-ca Quarl je upravo dosla 
u Parz,radimo interviju..

